{"tid":1562662,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我老豆支持香港人抗爭","createTime":"2019-09-12T06:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T14:36:32.000Z","uid":262802,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a451bb9ff289c382868d535eeb1e6c90d6aabbea","tid":1562662,"uid":262802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:01:33.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係廣州人又來啦。之前我喺連登支持過反送中，又喺香港過境翻廣州，過海關果陣真係好驚海關會查我手機拉我，好在無事，宜家我又翻到台灣讀書了<br />\n          翻左屋企同老豆傾反送中D野，所以順便分享下我老豆D思想：<br />\n1.香港人出來抗爭係為左對抗中共極權，推翻埋中共就啱咖了。中國人比人洗曬腦，成日叫香港抗爭D人做廢青。<br />\n2.共產黨唔係好人，一直愚民弱民。美國係自由世界嘅領導國，無左美國天下就大亂<br />\n3.好欣賞孫中山講嘅世界潮流浩浩蕩蕩，普世價值就係世界嘅潮流<br />\n<br />\n大家可以評價下，傾傾計"},{"pid":"959ffe7c2ce3281d4899075c4b53668440b17a21","tid":1562662,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:02:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"d308d65766094203d847f01ce3b5734b024c8691","tid":1562662,"uid":265824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"你亞爸咩年紀,點解腦筋咁清醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fddab2ea2b255f225c0b39efb0d61a4012c278","tid":1562662,"uid":262802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d308d65766094203d847f01ce3b5734b024c8691","tid":1562662,"uid":2658